{"sequence":26,"timestamp":"2026-04-30T09:46:53.553880046Z","event_type":"amendment_queued","details":{"amendment_id":"fr-1-d1857c23","body":"`src/contexts/bead_workflow/pr_watch.rs:376` fetches PR review comments with a single `gh api` call, and `src/contexts/bead_workflow/pr_watch.rs:434`-`439` never passes `--paginate`. GitHub returns only the first page by default, so a PR with more than one page of review comments can have a new codex bot line finding that this watcher never sees; the code can then reach the merge path at `src/contexts/bead_workflow/pr_watch.rs:254`. Paginate and flatten the reactions/comments responses, with a regression test where the bot comment is not on page one.","classification":"fix_current_bead","dedup_key":"0a2bd038ee6a5cdecf026b71d10ae5f85d1b5a19c45d43b45943c95881c98f82","reviewer_sources":[{"backend_family":"codex","model_id":"gpt-5.5-xhigh","reviewer_id":"reviewer-1"}],"run_id":"run-20260430082849","source":"workflow_stage","source_stage":"final_review"}}
{"sequence":27,"timestamp":"2026-04-30T09:46:53.577155158Z","event_type":"amendment_queued","details":{"amendment_id":"fr-1-a6add15f","body":"The known-flake rerun path matches the static flake test name against status-check names only: `src/contexts/bead_workflow/pr_watch.rs:517` stores the check `name`, and `src/contexts/bead_workflow/pr_watch.rs:303`-`307` compares those strings to `KNOWN_CI_FLAKES`. The repository's Actions job is named `Build, Test, and Conformance Gate` in `.github/workflows/conformance.yml:11`, so a failure of `adapters::br_process::tests::check_available_times_out_when_version_probe_hangs` will surface as that job/check name in `statusCheckRollup` and will be treated as non-flake. The watcher needs to inspect failed run logs or another source that contains failed test names before deciding whether to rerun.","classification":"fix_current_bead","dedup_key":"e39fbb52be387c35a2955a386860f767702d1eb508d5c7c7fb69bebeec83aee9","reviewer_sources":[{"backend_family":"codex","model_id":"gpt-5.5-xhigh","reviewer_id":"reviewer-1"}],"run_id":"run-20260430082849","source":"workflow_stage","source_stage":"final_review"}}
